OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,FThe daughter of a woman whose body has
OL,7,Fnot been found after she was murdered
OL,8,Fby her abusive boyfriend has described
OL,9,Fher restless nights not knowing where
OL,10,Fher mother's remains are.
OL,12,FFiona Holm, 48, was killed by handyman
OL,13,FCarl Cooper, 66, at his flat in
OL,14,FCatford, south-east London, on June 20
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FHe was jailed for life in July this
OL,18,Fyear for her murder and for killing
OL,19,Fanother former partner Naomi Hunte,
OL,20,F41, who was stabbed to death on
OL,21,FValentine's Day 2022.
