OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,FIn a statement issued through the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police, Ms Holm's
OL,8,Fdaughter Savannah Holm-Aderemi said:
OL,9,F"This year is the second Christmas
OL,10,Fwithout my beloved mother.
OL,12,F"As the heartache still continues, the
OL,13,Frestless nights go on knowing that she
OL,14,Fhas been out there this long, and no-
OL,15,Fone has come forward with any
OL,16,Finformation, which I find disturbing.
OL,18,F"The thought of us finding her remains
OL,19,Fis sickening to think about, but this
OL,20,Fwould also bring my whole family peace.
