OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,F"My nan has not been the same since.
OL,7,FThe only thing she worries about is
OL,8,Fwhere her daughter is, as she wants
OL,9,Fher to be found. Nan misses her
OL,10,Fdaughter's big heart and kind ways the
OL,11,Fmost."
OL,13,FA reward of #20,000 is on offer for
OL,14,Finformation leading to the discovery
OL,15,Fof Ms Holm's remains.
