OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Kate
OL,7,FBlackburn said: "My team has carried
OL,8,Fout a huge amount of work to try to
OL,9,Ffind Fiona, using specialist teams to
OL,10,Fsearch areas she was known to
OL,11,Ffrequent, open spaces, bodies of
OL,12,Fwater, houses, cars and lockups.
OL,14,F"Thousands of hours of CCTV has been
OL,15,Fseized and viewed, substantial mobile
OL,16,Fphone enquiries have been reviewed and
OL,17,Fhundreds of witness statements have
OL,18,Fbeen taken, including interviews with
OL,19,FFiona's family and friends. Those
OL,20,Fefforts have continued since Cooper's
OL,21,Fconviction.
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU
