OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,F"This Christmas, our thoughts are with
OL,7,FFiona's family, who are still waiting
OL,8,Ffor answers almost two years after her
OL,9,Ftragic murder. Our thoughts are also
OL,10,Fwith Naomi's family at this difficult
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"I am appealing to anybody who may be
OL,14,Fable to assist the ongoing search for
OL,15,FFiona's remains to come forward, no
OL,16,Fmatter how insignificant you think
OL,17,Fyour information could be. Perhaps now
OL,18,FCooper has been convicted, you feel
OL,19,Fable to come forward and tell us what
OL,20,Fyou know or have heard."
