OL,3,CDaughter suffers 'restless nights' as
OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,FWatchdog the Independent Office for
OL,7,FPolice Conduct is investigating how
OL,8,Fthe Met handled complaints made by
OL,9,Fboth women about the abuse they
OL,10,Fsuffered at Cooper's hands.
OL,12,FA spokesman said: "We have begun an
OL,13,Findependent investigation into
OL,14,Fcomplaints relating to the deaths of
OL,15,FNaomi Hunte and Fiona Holm, who were
OL,16,Fmurdered by Carl Cooper.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
