OL,4,Csearch for mother's remains continues
OL,6,F"In October 2024, we received
OL,7,Freferrals from the Met of complaints
OL,8,Fmade by the families of both victims,
OL,9,Falleging serious shortcomings in the
OL,10,Fforce's investigations prior to their
OL,11,Fdeaths.
OL,13,F"Our investigation, which is in its
OL,14,Fearly stages, will look at prior
OL,15,Fpolice contact relating to both
OL,16,Fvictims."
